</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-62_ pf-text-1"><strong>Community awareness programs</strong> - Initiate or participate in programs that aim to increase public awareness about the importance and safety of using AEDs on children.






































